@F flow-spec opus 2026-01-08
  Anchor:
    Format: @F <topic> <agent> <date>
    Position: First line, no indent
  Structure:
    Indent: 2 spaces per level
    Hierarchy: Indent depth = nesting depth
    Siblings: Same indent = same level
  Headers:
    Format: Name followed by colon
    Content: Indented lines beneath belong to header
  References:
    Location: ~42: description (tilde + line number)
    Cross-ref: -> @ref(topic) for inline links
    Deps: @uses: [list] at end of block
  Content:
    Lines: Plain text under headers
    Multiline: Same indent = continuation of thought
  Understanding Docs:
    Purpose: What it does and WHY it matters
    Key Functions: ~line: name() - behavior
    Design: Choices and their reasons
    Gotchas: Things that will bite you
